  }, "v27"), mdx("p", null, "H\xE3y xem lo\xE0i hoa hu\u1EC7; ch\xFAng n\xF3 ch\u1EB3ng v\u1EA5t v\u1EA3 c\u0169ng kh\xF4ng may m\u1EB7c g\xEC, nh\u01B0ng ta cho c\xE1c con bi\u1EBFt l\xE0 d\xF9 vua S\xF4-l\xF4-m\xF4n gi\xE0u sang \u0111\u1EBFn \u0111\xE2u \u0111i n\u1EEFa c\u0169ng ch\u01B0a \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c m\u1EB7c \u0111\u1EB9p b\u1EB1ng m\u1ED9t trong nh\u1EEFng \u0111\xF3a hoa hu\u1EC7 \u1EA5y. "), mdx("h6", {
